com.nathcat.peoplecat_server.WebSocketHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable, org.java_websocket.WebSocketListener
public class WebSocketHandler extends org.java_websocket.server.WebSocketServer
Acts as an alternative to the Server class. This class uses websockets to handle connections to clients, where the Server class uses native TCP connections.
Author:
Nathan Baines
